{"tid":1472023,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［和理非］自亂陣腳，你就輸成世！","createTime":"2019-08-14T12:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T12:54:59.000Z","uid":277853,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"16c8d4932ebd03aac3f6457c88aba28281568988","tid":1472023,"uid":277853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:24:27.000Z","msg":"（有朋友喺whatsapp group share左 「D4 之言」(sorry 條link唔係原Po) <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1462451\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1462451</a>出嚟，問大家點睇。有個平時唔聲唔聲嘅女仔竟然回咗，我覺得幾啱一眾和理非睇！）<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;轉&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n我覺得唔好睇咁多「分析」「拆局」。<br />\n<br />\n分享少少個人感受。<br />\n<br />\n可能係呢幾個禮拜發生太多事，大家會好傷心同忿怒，亦開始諗件事可以點解決。發展到呢個位，睇到一日之內發生咁多事，亦有啲事係過左自己原本嘅底線，<span style=\"color: red;\">不免開始軟弱，開始想搵way out，亦有少少動搖。</span><br />\n<br />\n尤其呢兩日機場嘅假消息，有份走/有份相信/有份傳開去，就發現原來大家都係真心驚。喺咁驚嘅情況下，你下次仲夠唔夠膽出去/積極參與？<br />\n<br />\n除咗驚政府警察，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>仲開始驚運動變質。</strong></span>對於有一刻見到對家話布袋彈射眼係假，我不斷搵番唔同嘅新聞片段去「求真」，我擔心到覺得內疚同自責。開始諗，其實我唔係「理性」，而係「動搖」。但過程中見到一句<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「你要信自己」</span></span>，就知道真係要重整吓自己。<br />\n<br />\n眾多嘅分析/政府內部消息同拆局，我會形容為「雲霧」。無論評論者嘅身份幾權威都好，你嘅目標一早喺度，只要撥開晒呢啲雲霧，條路本身就係咁行。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">行返自己條路就得！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">政府本身就要聽市民聲音，民意覺得佢冇正面回應就要政府好好正視。唔係因為政府覺得佢自己回應咗，我哋就要跟住佢走，訂另一個目標。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢一刻我哋應該堅持，<span style=\"color: red;\">認清番自己一開始個目標，好好行埋去。</span><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;完&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n和理非嘅你，準備好繼續行未？"},{"pid":"b90210a574a6335c22233e9389b0eee35f733e91","tid":1472023,"uid":277853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:24:43.000Z","msg":"P牌自推"},{"pid":"adf4b9e5dac19f8bed06a96ab449a3630b49a855","tid":1472023,"uid":268213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:25:02.000Z","msg":"求大家幫推818 post"},{"pid":"7eff842d1ef01726d6b28ec14b3813a895f91caf","tid":1472023,"uid":277853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:25:03.000Z","msg":"P牌自推"},{"pid":"8ec1386fade0da6b10666918ac8a31f39da3e370","tid":1472023,"uid":277853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:25:16.000Z","msg":"P牌自推"},{"pid":"7b769dbb376847f1eed3c4f04bf9f6e25651d203","tid":1472023,"uid":277853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:25:34.000Z","msg":"P牌自推"},{"pid":"59d77ed60970a9eb3dddab8c6df484cbe4712010","tid":1472023,"uid":277853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:25:47.000Z","msg":"P牌自推"},{"pid":"274839942b1704ff72a82b7da299db9287b5d490","tid":1472023,"uid":277853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:25:58.000Z","msg":"P牌自推"},{"pid":"55019b1a3e60bc4e71db67d4e646f9c9dad612e7","tid":1472023,"uid":277853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:26:08.000Z","msg":"P牌自推"},{"pid":"e771f51d107a5c485510f35f3d19e62cdd1eb971","tid":1472023,"uid":277853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:26:21.000Z","msg":"P牌自推"},{"pid":"6eab9a18f850df9e60b23229e690abe9ceb09b8e","tid":1472023,"uid":277853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:26:31.000Z","msg":"P牌自推"},{"pid":"6a0cb914f4e61489887f6c7c30c8cf33896bed65","tid":1472023,"uid":277853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:26:43.000Z","msg":"10呀！！！！"},{"pid":"24f89158a9ff8e7b3b6e50294299c0f217e14d89","tid":1472023,"uid":173844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:54:59.000Z","msg":"唔好自己動搖自己，勿忘初衷！"}]}